column2: p1 <- ggplot(salcha.DO.pred, aes(x = solar.time)) + geom_point(aes(y=DO.obs, colour = "Observed DO"), color = "darkcyan") + geom_line(aes(y = DO.mod, colour= "Modeled DO"), color = "blue4") + theme(axis.text.x=element_blank(), axis.ticks.x=element_blank(), axis.title.x=element_blank() ) + labs(colour="Green", y = "DO (mg/L)") +  theme(legend.position="none") + ggtitle("Observed (points) and Modeled (lines)")
